OL,3,C'End the delays': MP urges ministers
OL,4,Cto continue with Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FAn MP has urged the government to "end
OL,7,Fthe delays" on a Hillsborough Law
OL,8,Fafter ministers agreed to carry the
OL,9,Flong-awaited legislation over to the
OL,10,Fnext parliamentary session.
OL,12,FLabour's Ian Byrne, who was at
OL,13,FHillsborough when 97 Liverpool
OL,14,Ffootball fans were killed, welcomed
OL,15,Fthe commitment but urged the
OL,16,FGovernment to "end the delays".
OL,26,@xD@OOUxD@^O]
