OL,3,C'End the delays': MP urges ministers
OL,4,Cto continue with Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer had
OL,7,Fpromised to deliver the draft law,
OL,8,Fformally known as the Public Office
OL,9,F(Accountability) Bill, by 15 April
OL,10,F2025, to mark the 36th anniversary of
OL,11,Fthe disaster.
OL,13,FHowever, progress was stalled
OL,14,Ffollowing concerns over changes which
OL,15,Fcould see the proposed duty of candour
OL,16,Fdisapplied to intelligence agencies.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
