OL,3,C'End the delays': MP urges ministers
OL,4,Cto continue with Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FIn the Commons on 23 April, Mr Byrne,
OL,7,Fthe MP for Liverpool West Derby,
OL,8,Fcalled for urgency and pressed
OL,9,Fministers to "deliver the law in full
OL,10,Fwithout carve outs".
OL,12,FCommons Leader Sir Alan Campbell had
OL,13,Fearlier told MPs Hillsborough Law
OL,14,Fwould be subject to a carry-over
OL,15,Fmotion on Monday 27 April.
OL,17,FIf agreed to by the Commons the Bill
OL,18,Fas it stands will be passed over to
OL,19,Fthe next session.
OL,26,@qD@NOUrD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
