OL,3,C'End the delays': MP urges ministers
OL,4,Cto continue with Hillsborough Law
OL,6,FLabour pledged to introduce a
OL,7,FHillsborough Law ` to require public
OL,8,Fofficials to tell the truth during
OL,9,Finquiries and investigations ` in its
OL,10,F2024 manifesto.
OL,12,FThe Government faced a row after
OL,13,Fproposing amendments that would see
OL,14,Fspies brought within the scope of the
OL,15,Flaw, but only with the approval of the
OL,16,Fhead of their services.
OL,18,FCampaigners warned this could be used
OL,19,Fas a way of escaping the new duty of
OL,20,Fcandour and the amendments were pulled
OL,21,Fat the eleventh hour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
