PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776971469
OL,3,C'End the delays': MP urges ministers
OL,4,Cto continue with Hillsborough Law
OL,6,F"Ministers must end the delays and
OL,7,Fdeliver the law in full without carve
OL,8,Fouts for the intelligence and security
OL,9,Fservices, as promised, to achieve the
OL,10,Fcultural change the country
OL,11,Fdesperately needs, as we've seen this
OL,12,Fweek.
OL,14,F"Can I also ask (Sir Alan) to remind
OL,15,Fsome in Government that negative media
OL,16,Fbriefings against key figures in the
OL,17,Fcampaign risks undermining confidence
OL,18,Fin the process and should cease?
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776971469
OL,3,C'End the delays': MP urges ministers
OL,4,Cto continue with Hillsborough Law
OL,6,F"And following the Prime Minister's
OL,7,Fcommitment at PMQs, last week, I ask
OL,8,F(Sir Alan) to ensure I am directly
OL,9,Finformed, included in all meetings and
OL,10,Fbriefings moving forward as the
OL,11,Fparliamentary lead for the
OL,12,FHillsborough law."
OL,14,FSir Alan replied: "I know that he has
OL,15,Fa personal interest, as someone who
OL,16,Fwas at Hillsborough on that terrible
OL,17,Fday.
OL,19,F"As he says, we brought forward the
OL,20,Fcarryover motion, and I'm pleased that
OL,21,Fhe welcomes that.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@RO]vD@SOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
